[
    {
        "Key": 1,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "虚构的怪物在模拟空间中湮灭。眼前的画面定格，变成雪花，然后被完全的黑暗所笼罩。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 2,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这几天几乎一直待在模拟舱里。睁开眼，连训练室的光线也变得刺眼。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 3,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "——终于结束了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 4,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我叫playername，现在在<snowbreak>世界树公司</>担任分析员一职，同时也是<snowbreak>海姆达尔部队</>的最高长官。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 5,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "两周前接到消息，朔州的<snowbreak>“树”</>发生了异动。为此，公司策划了拔除“树”的行动，我和队员们为此开始了长达两周的环境压力训练。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 6,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从模拟舱中坐起，撑着头。有手伸过来，一边搭在我的肩头，另一边慢慢揉着我的眉头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 7,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl002_01",
        "zh_CN": "辛苦了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 8,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是里芙的声音，我的队员，也是最亲密的人之一。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 9,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "只要下达命令，她就会毫不犹豫地执行、完成。我们不知道一起度过了多少次难关。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 10,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我依旧闭着眼睛，握住她的手，覆在眼上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 11,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没办法的事。也许是舍塔刺激了“树”……那次行动之后，朔州的“树”就像疯了似的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 12,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl002_02",
        "zh_CN": "那个疯子，她迟早有一天要付出代价。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 13,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你感觉怎么样？九十八次模拟训练，一开始真没想到能撑到这个数字。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 14,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl002_03",
        "zh_CN": "我很好。这种高压训练也是一种变强的途径。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 15,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这次是针对“树”的特殊训练，以后还是少这样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 16,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "过度疲劳消耗太大了。我感觉现在合上眼就能睡着。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 17,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl002_04",
        "zh_CN": "嗯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 18,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl008_01",
        "zh_CN": "达令——我准备了蛋糕，吃点再睡吧？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮的声音传了过来。我睁开眼，透过指缝，看见她从房间门口探着头。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她也是我最亲密的人，走到哪里都是耀眼的存在——哪怕是在战场上。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不论面对什么困难，她都像一团火一样，见不着一点儿气馁和颓丧。只是看着她，就让我疲惫的精神又有了一股力量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "端到休息室去吧，一起吃。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "对里芙笑了笑，站起身。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 24,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "换个衣服，洗个澡什么的。半个小时之后休息室集合。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 25,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl008_02",
        "zh_CN": "那我先放冰箱里~",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 26,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "芬妮端着蛋糕回去了，只剩下里芙和我在房间里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 27,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你去修整一下吧。安卡希雅不知道去哪了……我去喊吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 28,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "里芙点了点头，转身往外走。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 29,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "等等——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "从身后抱住了她。她轻轻嗯了一声——虽然背对着我，但我能察觉到她嘴角的笑意。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "辛苦了，亲爱的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她转过身，抱着我，把头靠在我的胸口，没有说话。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "额头抵着下巴，这么温存了一会儿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl002_05",
        "zh_CN": "休息室等你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "在附近转了一圈儿，依然没找到安卡希雅。在回房间拿通讯终端的路上，她却从走廊尽头拐了出来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "安卡希雅——看着年纪不大。实际上……因为一些变故，她曾在休眠舱里睡了三十年。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "是我把她从睡眠舱里唤醒的。用三十年前的话说，她是个宅女——不善言谈，除了跟我在一起的时候。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 39,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "相处的时间长了之后，她有事没事都喜欢跑到我旁边待着，就像现在——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 40,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "跑哪去了？半天没找着你。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 41,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl001_01",
        "zh_CN": "游戏的日常没清，跑回去清了一下。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 42,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "休息室有蛋糕，一会儿一起去吃？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 43,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl001_02",
        "zh_CN": "嗯，我看见芬妮的消息了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 44,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她顺势跟在我身后，一路进了我的房间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 45,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl001_03",
        "zh_CN": "这次任务结束之后，就把《双人奇行》打完吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 46,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……你一定要在出发前夜说这种话吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 47,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl001_04",
        "zh_CN": "要怪就怪你太忙，我还有很多想和你一起做的事呢。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 48,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没别的事我就先洗澡了……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 49,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl001_05",
        "zh_CN": "你随意，我在你这眯一小会儿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 50,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl001_06",
        "zh_CN": "我洗过澡了哦，衣服也是新换的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 51,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她甩掉鞋子，一头钻进我的被子里，只露出一个脑袋来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 52,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl001_07",
        "zh_CN": "怎么不脱了？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 53,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员战斗",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……你在打什么坏主意呢？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 54,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl001_08",
        "zh_CN": "我能有什么坏心思……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 55,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没理会她，脱了衣服走进了淋浴间。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 56,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "冷水带着冷意，从头顶一路钻到脚底，和骨肉中的疲乏缠在一起，又一点一点剥落、洗清。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 57,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "擦干净身子，躺进被窝里。安卡希雅并没有睡，而是侧着身子，看着我的眼睛。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 58,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl001_09",
        "zh_CN": "还有多久集合？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 59,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "二十分钟。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 60,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她的眼睛往下瞄了一眼，又脸不红心不跳、直勾勾地盯了回来。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 61,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "……你想干嘛？这点时间不够的……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 62,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "安卡希雅病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl001_10",
        "zh_CN": "好吧，那就眯一会儿。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 63,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她钻到我怀里，把头埋在我的脖颈间。头发上有洗发露的味道，鼻息一点点推着颈间的皮肤，痒痒的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 64,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "萌生的悸动被柔软的拥抱按下了——就这么抱着就很好了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 65,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "闭上眼，小憩了一会儿。直到敲门声响起——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 66,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl008_03",
        "zh_CN": "达令~你在里面吗——",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 67,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "怀里一空。睁开眼，安卡希雅已经不见了踪影，只剩下敞开的窗户。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 68,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "分析员无帽",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "进来吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 69,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl008_04",
        "zh_CN": "嘿——！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 70,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "一团金色簇到眼前。芬妮整个扑在我身上，刚洗完吹干的金发散在我脸上，然后便是热烈的吻。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 71,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "芬妮病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "Play_Vo_chp0ep1_girl008_05",
        "zh_CN": "是不是累坏了？要不要再睡会儿？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 72,
        "Flag": "",
